                            <comment id="12847127" author="bryanduxbury" created="Thu, 18 Mar 2010 21:49:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This patch implements the reset() strategy. It also makes sure that partialDeserialize throws TExceptions only, which makes it much easier to catch stuff coming out. Finally, it puts a protocol_.reset() in a finally block in all of the deserialize methods to make sure that stateful protocols will get cleaned up appropriately.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
